# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
we have to store roman values first at a place to calculate the value
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
Stored elements in hashmap
traversed string from back,if current element is of less value than the prev(case:"IV") we subtract current number from are answer otherwise(case:"C") add it we also store the prev elements value in a prev to make decision
# Complexity
- Time complexity:
