# Converter for Roman numbers
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

# Approach
Translating numbers from the end
Runtime Beats ~88.00% (93% - 79%).
Mamory Beats ~ 99%
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)
